270
00:20:05,943 --> 00:20:08,356
Julia... honey.

271
00:20:08,521 --> 00:20:10,155
Now, be a good girl.

272
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:11,887
Level with me.

273
00:20:12,562 --> 00:20:15,048
It's not just my pelvis, is it?

274
00:20:23,055 --> 00:20:24,963
